label: carriedTransportEquipment
comment: A piece of transport equipment carried on this piece of logistics transport equipment, such as a container placed on a rail wagon.

rangeIncludes.comment: A piece of transport equipment that is associated with another piece of transport equipment, such as a maritime container placed on a rail wagon for transportation.
